{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u3010Story\u3011</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a world where humans and the conscious beings known as Kururu coexist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The study of the essence and mechanisms of Kururu has not yet reached any conclusions that have achieved widespread consensus. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, it is generally agreed that it is a form of life that exists in harmony and resonance with all human mental and physiological rhythms, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">capable of interacting with humans during cognition, thought, or communication. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Humans must maintain a benign balance with Kururu to ensure the stability of their sanity and cognitive abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, only a very few humans can visually identify, physically perceive, and manipulate Kururu, and conduct systematic research on them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We call these individuals &quot;Tuners.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This summer, Mioi (barely) passed the professional exam and came to Baixiang City as an apprentice Tuner, along with Kasula and Syss.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a coastal city with nearly two centuries of history but not much communication with the outside world, which, however, has attracted the attention of the Tuners Association in the past decade. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the routine tasks were carried out, this metropolis began to exhibit abnormalities, with phenomena of group dysregulation becoming increasingly common and severe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the same time, two mysterious Tuners who had received special commissions also arrived in Baixiang City... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/\u6d77\u62a5-1_en.jpg?t=1737018921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u3010Exploration\u3011</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u00b7 Unravel the Secrets of Baixiang City</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  Gain unique encounters through random routes, with each successful patrol bringing you closer to the &quot;truth.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/\u63a2\u7d22\u6848\u4f8b-\u63a2\u7d22.gif?t=1737018921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/\u63a2\u7d22\u6848\u4f8b-1\u5bf9\u8bdd.gif?t=1737018921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u00b7 Card-based City Patrol</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  Flip through the perilous mission cards, respond carefully, and make the best adventurous decisions for your team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/\u6d77\u62a5-2_en.jpg?t=1737018921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u3010Combat\u3011</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u00b7 Magical Girls Forging Ahead</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  Execute splendid combos with a single click, block at the right moment, and engage in fast-paced combat that's simple in attack and defense but infinitely variable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/\u63a2\u7d22\u6848\u4f8b-\u5bf9\u6218.gif?t=1737018921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/\u6d77\u62a5-3_en.jpg?t=1737018921\" 